                        th Position
                        th Name
                        th Email
                tbody
                    each member in locals.board_members
                        tr
                            td= member.position
                            td= member.name
                            td: span.email= member.email
    .row.alumni
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2#alumni
            h1 Alumni
            p In October 2011, the Tartan Crew Alumni Network (TCAN) was launched! Alumni, parents, and friends are in the process of creating a vibrant alumni network for the Carnegie Mellon University Rowing Club (CMURC). The shape and direction of the network are still in the beta-stage, however the overarching goal is to provide opportunities to:

    .row.alumni
        .col-sm-4
            p: b Connect with alumni
        .col-sm-4
            p: b Give back to the team
        .col-sm-4
            p: b Support the legacy of CMURC

    .row.alumni
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
            p The network is inclusive to: parents, coaches, advisors, staff, and alumni with any level of team association. If you have an affinity for the Carnegie Mellon University Rowing Club, we want you connected!

            p Learn more and join 
                a(href="http://alumni.cmu.edu/s/1410/alumni/index.aspx?sid=1410&gid=1&pgid=525") here
                | .
    .row.alumni
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
            p We'd also like to welcome the 2014 graduating varsity crewmembers to our alumni network!  We'd like to congratulate and thank the following for their years of dedication to the crew:

            table.well.table.table-bordered.table-striped
                thead
                    tr
                        th Name
                        th Major
                tbody
                    each member in locals.graduates
                        tr
                            td= member.name
                            td= member.major
    .row.donate
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2#donate
            h1 Donate
            p We are so appreciative to all of our generous donors! For those who are interested in giving back to the CMU Rowing Club, did you know you can donate online?!? You can do so easily by visiting the 
                a(href="https://securelb.imodules.com/s/1410/giving/form_hdr.aspx?sid=1410&gid=1&pgid=3769&cid=6028") annual giving website
                | . To designate a gift to the Rowing Club, select “other” from the drop-down menu and type “The University Rowing Club” in the comments box. Easy as that! We are so thankful for any and all support! 
